section.def:
appellant
                (上訴人) means a person whose notice of appeal is
            accepted under section 3;

Chairman
                (主席) means the person appointed as Chairman of
            the Licensing Appeals Board under section 125A(2)(a) of the Ordinance;

secretary
                (秘書) means the person appointed as secretary to
            the Licensing Appeals Board under section 125I(1)(a) of the Ordinance;
